When to use

Required setup: Every application using Nimbus components must include NimbusProvider at the root level. Without it, Nimbus components will not function.

Basic usage

``tsx
import { NimbusProvider } from "@commercetools/nimbus";

function App() {
  return (
    <NimbusProvider>
      <YourApp />
    </NimbusProvider>
  );
}
`

